data.description: ***Price Improvement**Want to SAVE over $400/month in their payment? Seller could be open to a 2/1 rate buy down with acceptable offer! Lovely 3/2 located in highly desirable community in Rock Hill/York County South Carolina. Home sits on a beautiful 1.3 acre, private, wooded lot and is situated on a quiet, cul-de-sac street. When you pull in, you will be captivated by the charm of this home.The inviting front porch is perfect for a morning cup of coffee or enjoying nature.As you walk in, you will be impressed with the huge great room with gas log fireplace.  The eat in kitchen opens to the great room. The 3 bedrooms are huge and hard to find in this size.Back yard is perfect with an oversized deck perfect for grilling, entertaining or just relaxing.This is a hard to find ranch, on over 1 acre, in a great neighborhood with highly desirable schools that you don't want to miss.  Easy access to 161/Celanese Rd. and Mt. Gallant Rd. Newport shopping and restaurants as well as downtown York.
